      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no chips, scratches, or dings to be found anywhere. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with every surface, button, and stitch remaining in like-new condition. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history, ensuring a smooth and powerful driving experience with no compromises.",
